      "*": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p><b><a href=\"/Main_Page\" title=\"Main Page\">Home</a> * <a href=\"/People\" title=\"People\">People</a> * Anthony Cozzie</b>\n</p>\n<div class=\"thumb tright\"><div class=\"thumbinner\" style=\"width:211px;\"><a href=\"http://www.acoz.net/\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/images/8/84/AnthonyCozzie.jpg\" width=\"209\" height=\"281\" class=\"thumbimage\" /></a>  <div class=\"thumbcaption\"><div class=\"magnify\"><a href=\"/File:AnthonyCozzie.jpg\" class=\"internal\" title=\"Enlarge\"></a></div>Anthony Cozzie <sup id=\"cite_ref-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></div></div></div> \n<p><b>Anthony E. Cozzie</b>,<br />\nan American computer scientist with a Ph.D. from <a href=\"/University_of_Illinois_at_Urbana-Champaign\" title=\"University of Illinois at Urbana-Champaign\">University of Illinois at Urbana-Champaign</a> on the topic of <i>Detecting and Combining Programming Patterns</i> <sup id=\"cite_ref-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>, creative thinker, intuitive programmer, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Cosmopolitan\">cosmopolitan</a> world traveler, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Erudition\">erudite</a> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Conversation\">conversationalist</a>, modest, all-around good guy <sup id=\"cite_ref-3\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup>. As retired computer chess programmer <sup id=\"cite_ref-4\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-4\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup> <sup id=\"cite_ref-5\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-5\">&#91;5&#93;</a></sup>, Anthony is author of the world class chess program <a href=\"/Zappa\" title=\"Zappa\">Zappa</a> <sup id=\"cite_ref-6\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-6\">&#91;6&#93;</a></sup> <sup id=\"cite_ref-7\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-7\">&#91;7&#93;</a></sup>, the winner of the <a href=\"/WCCC_2005\" title=\"WCCC 2005\">WCCC 2005</a> in <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Reykjav%C3%ADk\">Reykjavík</a>, and after the <a href=\"/Rybka\" title=\"Rybka\">Rybka</a> <a href=\"/World_Computer_Chess_Championship#RybkaDisqualification\" title=\"World Computer Chess Championship\">disqualification</a> in 2011, the <a href=\"/WCCC_2007\" title=\"WCCC 2007\">WCCC 2007</a> in <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Amsterdam\">Amsterdam</a>. \n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Photos_.26_Games\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Photos &amp; Games</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#Reykjav.C3.ADk_2005\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Reykjavík 2005</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#Mexico-City_2007\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Mexico-City 2007</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#Selected_Publications\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Selected Publications</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-5\"><a href=\"#Forum_Posts\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Forum Posts</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-6\"><a href=\"#External_Links\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">External Links</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-7\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">5</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Photos_.26_Games\">Photos &amp; Games</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Anthony_Cozzie&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" title=\"Edit section: Photos &amp; Games\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Reykjav.C3.ADk_2005\">Reykjavík 2005</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Anthony_Cozzie&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" title=\"Edit section: Reykjavík 2005\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"floatnone\"><a href=\"/File:Anthony2005.JPG\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"Anthony2005.JPG\" src=\"/images/7/79/Anthony2005.JPG\" width=\"640\" height=\"512\" style=\"vertical-align: text-bottom\" class=\"thumbborder\" /></a></div> \n<p><a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Anthony Cozzie</a> just before round 7, <a href=\"/Zappa\" title=\"Zappa\">Zappa</a> - <a href=\"/Junior\" title=\"Junior\">Junior</a>, <a href=\"/WCCC_2005\" title=\"WCCC 2005\">WCCC 2005</a> <sup id=\"cite_ref-8\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-8\">&#91;8&#93;</a></sup> <sup id=\"cite_ref-9\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-9\">&#91;9&#93;</a></sup> <sup id=\"cite_ref-10\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-10\">&#91;10&#93;</a></sup> \n</p>\n<pre>\n[Event \"WCCC 2005\"]\n[Site \"Reykjavík, Iceland\"]\n[Date \"2005.08.19\"]\n[Round \"7\"]\n[White \"Zappa\"]\n[Black \"Junior\"]\n[Result \"1-0\"]\n\n1.d4 d5 2.Nf3 Nf6 3.c4 e6 4.Nc3 c6 5.e3 Nbd7 6.Qc2 Bd6 7.g4 h6 \n8.Rg1 e5 9.cxd5 cxd5 10.g5 hxg5 11.Nxg5 e4 12.Nb5 Nb6 13.Bd2 Bf5 \n14.h3 Bh2 15.Rg2 Rc8 16.Qb3 Bb8 17.Bb4 Nh7 18.Nxh7 Rxh7 19.Rg1 Rc6 \n20.Nc3 a6 21.a4 Nc4 22.Bxc4 dxc4 23.Qc2 Rch6 24.Qe2 Qc8 25.O-O-O b5 \n26.d5 Qb7 27.d6 Bd7 28.axb5 axb5 29.Rg5 f5 30.Rd5 Qa8 31.Kb1 g6 \n32.Re5+ Kf7 33.Nd5 Kf8 34.Nf6 Rf7 35.Re8+ Kg7 36.Nh5+ Kh7 1-0\n</pre>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Mexico-City_2007\">Mexico-City 2007</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Anthony_Cozzie&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" title=\"Edit section: Mexico-City 2007\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"floatnone\"><a href=\"http://www.chesstigers.de/index_news.php?id=1269&amp;rubrik=3\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img alt=\"Mex7 Computer Kosic Levy Railich HWS.JPG\" src=\"/images/5/5a/Mex7_Computer_Kosic_Levy_Railich_HWS.JPG\" width=\"640\" height=\"439\" style=\"vertical-align: text-bottom\" class=\"thumbborder\" /></a></div> \n<p>Press conference <a href=\"/Zappa_versus_Rybka_2007\" title=\"Zappa versus Rybka 2007\">Zappa versus Rybka 2007</a>, Anthony Cozzie, <a href=\"/David_Levy\" title=\"David Levy\">David Levy</a> and <a href=\"/Vasik_Rajlich\" title=\"Vasik Rajlich\">Vasik Rajlich</a> <sup id=\"cite_ref-11\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-11\">&#91;11&#93;</a></sup> \n</p>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Selected_Publications\">Selected Publications</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Anthony_Cozzie&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" title=\"Edit section: Selected Publications\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<p><sup id=\"cite_ref-12\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-12\">&#91;12&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<ul><li> <a href=\"/Robert_Hyatt\" title=\"Robert Hyatt\">Robert Hyatt</a>, <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Anthony Cozzie</a> (<b>2005</b>). <i><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.craftychess.com/hyatt/collisions.html\">The Effect of Hash Signature Collisions in a Chess Program</a></i>. <a href=\"/ICGA_Journal#18_3\" title=\"ICGA Journal\">ICGA Journal, Vol. 28, No. 3</a> </li>\n<li> <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Anthony Cozzie</a> (<b>2007</b>). <i>Zappa vs. Rybka</i>. <a href=\"/ICGA_Journal#30_4\" title=\"ICGA Journal\">ICGA Journal, Vol. 30, No. 4</a></li>\n<li> <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Anthony Cozzie</a>, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.informatik.uni-trier.de/~ley/db/indices/a-tree/s/Stratton:Frank.html\">Frank Stratton</a>, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.informatik.uni-trier.de/~ley/db/indices/a-tree/x/Xue:Hui.html\">Hui Xue</a>, <a href=\"/Mathematician#STKing\" title=\"Mathematician\">Samuel T. King</a> (<b>2008</b>). <i>Digging for Data Structures</i>. <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.informatik.uni-trier.de/~ley/db/conf/osdi/osdi2008.html#CozzieSXK08\">OSDI 2008</a>, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.usenix.org/event/osdi08/tech/full_papers/cozzie/cozzie.pdf\">pdf</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Mathematician#STKing\" title=\"Mathematician\">Samuel T. King</a>, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://opera.ucsd.edu/~tucek/\">Joseph Tucek</a>, <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Anthony Cozzie</a>, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.informatik.uni-trier.de/~ley/db/indices/a-tree/g/Grier:Chris.html\">Chris Grier</a>, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://cn.linkedin.com/in/weihangjiang\">Weihang Jiang</a>, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.jacobsschool.ucsd.edu/faculty/faculty_bios/index.sfe?fmp_recid=317\">Yuanyuan Zhou</a> (<b>2008</b>). <i>Designing and Implementing Malicious Hardware</i>. <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.informatik.uni-trier.de/~ley/db/conf/nsdi/leet2008.html#KingTCGJZ08\">LEET 2008</a>, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.cs.uiuc.edu/homes/kingst/Research_files/king08.pdf\">pdf</a></li>\n<li> <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Anthony Cozzie</a> (<b>2011</b>). <i>The Future of Computer Chess</i>. <a href=\"/Selective_Search\" title=\"Selective Search\">Selective Search</a> 154, pp. 11, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.chesscomputeruk.com/SS_154.pdf\">pdf</a> hosted by <a href=\"/Mike_Watters\" title=\"Mike Watters\">Mike Watters</a></li>\n<li> <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Anthony Cozzie</a> (<b>2011</b>). <i><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.ideals.illinois.edu/handle/2142/24358\">Detecting and Combining Programming Patterns</a></i>. Ph.D. thesis, <a href=\"/University_of_Illinois_at_Urbana-Champaign\" title=\"University of Illinois at Urbana-Champaign\">University of Illinois at Urbana-Champaign</a>, advisor <a href=\"/Mathematician#STKing\" title=\"Mathematician\">Samuel T. King</a></li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Forum_Posts\">Forum Posts</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Anthony_Cozzie&amp;action=edit&amp;section=5\" title=\"Edit section: Forum Posts\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=278632\">Zappa CCT5 Report</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Anthony Cozzie</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, January 21, 2003&#160;» <a href=\"/CCT5\" title=\"CCT5\">CCT5</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=346423\">Zappa @ CCT6</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Anthony Cozzie</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, February 01, 2004&#160;» <a href=\"/CCT6\" title=\"CCT6\">CCT6</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=363519\">The Zappa Attack Table Code</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Anthony Cozzie</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, May 05, 2004</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=419900\">Re: Fruit fly races</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Anthony Cozzie</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, April 06, 2005</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=444686\">Zappa scaling #s</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Anthony Cozzie</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, August 23, 2005</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=447511\">Re: Zappa Retail: No UCI?</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Anthony Cozzie</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, September 04, 2005</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=469523\">Re: what do we know about zappa</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Anthony Cozzie</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, December 12, 2005</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=472806\">Zappa Hardware Upgrade</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Anthony Cozzie</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, December 23, 2005</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=475497\">Zappa Report</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Anthony Cozzie</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, December 30, 2005&#160;» <a href=\"/IPCCC_2005_b\" title=\"IPCCC 2005 b\">IPCCC 2005 b</a></li></ul>\n<dl><dd> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=475521\">Re: Zappa Report</a> by <a href=\"/Ingo_Alth%C3%B6fer\" title=\"Ingo Althöfer\">Ingo Althöfer</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, December 30, 2005 <sup id=\"cite_ref-13\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-13\">&#91;13&#93;</a></sup></dd></dl>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://rybkaforum.net/cgi-bin/rybkaforum/topic_show.pl?tid=3006;pg=4\">Re: Strelka 2.0 pg 4</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Anthony Cozzie</a>, <a href=\"/Computer_Chess_Forums\" title=\"Computer Chess Forums\">Rybka Forum</a>, January 11, 2008</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://rybkaforum.net/cgi-bin/rybkaforum/topic_show.pl?tid=3172\">Anthony Cozzie speak&#160;!</a> by Silvian, <a href=\"/Computer_Chess_Forums\" title=\"Computer Chess Forums\">Rybka Forum</a>, February 03, 2008 </li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=23313\">My two cents</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Anthony Cozzie</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, August 27, 2008</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=38440\">Longer Article</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Anthony Cozzie</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, March 17, 2011</li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"External_Links\">External Links</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Anthony_Cozzie&amp;action=edit&amp;section=6\" title=\"Edit section: External Links\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.game-ai-forum.org/icga-tournaments/person.php?id=53\">Anthony Cozzie's ICGA Tournaments</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.acoz.net/\">Anthony Cozzie's page</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.chessbase.com/newsdetail.asp?newsid=3043\">World Computer Chess Champion: Zap!Chess</a> by <a href=\"/ChessBase\" title=\"ChessBase\">ChessBase</a>, April 13, 2006</li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Anthony_Cozzie&amp;action=edit&amp;section=7\" title=\"Edit section: References\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap mw-references-columns\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-1\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.acoz.net/\">Anthony Cozzie's page</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-2\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Anthony Cozzie</a> (<b>2011</b>). <i><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.ideals.illinois.edu/handle/2142/24358\">Detecting and Combining Programming Patterns</a></i>. Ph.D. thesis, <a href=\"/University_of_Illinois_at_Urbana-Champaign\" title=\"University of Illinois at Urbana-Champaign\">University of Illinois at Urbana-Champaign</a>, advisor <a href=\"/Mathematician#STKing\" title=\"Mathematician\">Samuel T. King</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-3\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-3\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.acoz.net/cv_acozzie.pdf\">CV Anthony Cozzie</a> (pdf)</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-4\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-4\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.acoz.net/zappa/#retirement\">Zappa - Retirement</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-5\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-5\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=479353\">Subject: CCC Retirement</a> by <i>Zappa</i>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, January 13, 2006</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-6\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-6\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://netfiles.uiuc.edu/acozzie2/www/zappa/\">Zappa Chess Engine</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-7\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-7\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Zappa_%28chess%29\">Chessprogram Zappa from Wikipedia</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-8\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-8\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\">Photo by <a href=\"/Gerd_Isenberg\" title=\"Gerd Isenberg\">Gerd Isenberg</a>, August 19, 2005</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-9\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-9\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=443224\">Zappa - Junior</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Anthony Cozzie</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, August 19, 2005</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-10\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-10\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.game-ai-forum.org/icga-tournaments/round.php?tournament=21&amp;round=7&amp;id=3\">Reykjavík 2005 - Chess - Round 7 - Game 3 (ICGA Tournaments)</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-11\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-11\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.chesstigers.de/index_news.php?id=1269&amp;rubrik=3\">WM Mexiko-City 2007: 108 Bilder, Namen, Themen, kommentiert, ...</a> (German) <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.chesstigers.de/index.php\">Chess Tigers News</a> October 08, 2007</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-12\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-12\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.informatik.uni-trier.